Q27. tr Convert file contents into uppercase , also learn "-s" option of this command
Sol:
aditya@aditya-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UF:~/OS_Assignments/Assign_3$ cat file4
Hello Aditya welcome to sunbeam

aditya@aditya-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UF:~/OS_Assignments/Assign_3$ cat file4|tr "a-z" "A-Z"
HELLO ADITYA WELCOME TO SUNBEAM

aditya@aditya-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UF:~/OS_Assignments/Assign_3$ cat file4
Hello                Aditya welcome             to           sunbeam

aditya@aditya-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UF:~/OS_Assignments/Assign_3$ cat file4|tr -s " " ","
Hello,Aditya,welcome,to,sunbeam
