Q28. cut Split the file contents using delimiter and print required fields
Sol:
aditya@aditya-VivoBook-15-ASUS-Laptop-X507UF:~/OS_Assignments/Assign_4$ cat data.txt|tr " " ","|cut -d "," -f1,2
